---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About | Raluca's Beauty Corner">

  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px 40px 80px;">

    <p style="font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple);margin-bottom:16px;font-weight:500;">✦ About</p>

    <h1 style="font-family:var(--ff-serif);font-size:52px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.12;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:32px;">
      Hi, I'm <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--purple);">Raluca</em>
    </h1>

    <div style="width:90px;height:90px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--purple-mid),var(--purple-lt));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--ff-serif);font-size:36px;font-weight:300;color:var(--purple-dk);margin-bottom:36px;">R</div>

    <div style="font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.95;color:var(--ink-mid);font-weight:300;">
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Welcome to my little corner of the internet dedicated to all things beauty — especially the looks that defined the 90s and why they still feel so right today.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        I'm obsessed with cool-toned makeup: the kind with lavender undertones, frosted finishes, dusty mauves, and that particular icy shimmer that makes you look like you just stepped off a 1997 music video set. In the best way possible.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        This blog is where I write about makeup trends, share tutorials, review products, and explore the nostalgia of 90s beauty — from overlined lips to frosty eyeshadow to the perfect cool brown liner.
      </p>
      <blockquote style="border-left:3px solid var(--purple-lt);margin:2.5rem 0;padding:1.2rem 1.8rem;background:var(--purple-bg);font-family:var(--ff-serif);font-size:22px;font-style:italic;color:var(--purple-dk);line-height:1.6;">
        Beauty is a mood. And my mood is perpetually 1997.
      </blockquote>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Expect honest reviews, proper technique breakdowns, and zero fluff.
      </p>
      <p>
        Thanks for being here. Now go find a frosted lipstick and wear it with confidence. ✦
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:48px;padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/blog" style="display:inline-block;font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;background:var(--purple);padding:12px 24px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;transition:background 0.2s;">Read the blog →</a>
      <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-block;font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple);border:1px solid var(--purple-lt);padding:12px 24px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">Follow on Instagram</a>
    </div>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>
